Verify that appending a newline only between lines is the intended behavior, especially if individual buffer lines may already end with a newline. Consider clarifying the expected formatting in a code comment to ensure future maintainers understand the decision.
```suggestion
      // Append a newline only if the current line does not already end with one.
      if (bufstrlen == 0 || bufstr[bufstrlen - 1] != '\n') {
        kv_push(contents, '\n');
      }
```

